{"tid":2071353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧：北京政權同爛仔無分別 企圖支配全世界","createTime":"2020-06-19T18:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T23:32:34.000Z","uid":53844,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b8cf440f629a517330fa6b5925177699ec2cfd79","tid":2071353,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:30:12.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧繼續大肆抨擊中國，聲言歐洲靠攏中國，將要放棄價值觀。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧透過視頻向丹麥人權會議發表談話時形容，北京有如流氓，企圖支配全球。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧表示，民主倚賴獨裁並不化算，形容中國對歐洲價值體系的挑戰已在各國首都，歐洲必須以懷疑態度，看待每宗中國國企投資，促請歐洲國家避免採用中國民企華為的設備。<br />\n<br />\n他透露，日前與中共中央政治局委員楊潔篪會談6小時，坦率向對方表達類似意見。蓬佩奧又強調，美國密切關注中印邊境局勢、新疆維吾爾族人問題及港區國安法立法。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-20 01:41:55<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533084-20200620.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533084-20200620.htm&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=a5125cd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533084-20200620.htm&h=8fcbb89a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533084-20200620.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8d813e07b86ddcd9cffdc5ecede6ab90c596ebf7","tid":2071353,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:31:32.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"1e1153117f874a9a360b420d5057f96b245aef0f","tid":2071353,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:32:30.000Z","msg":"直線抽撀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854c181e17b17fecba78ef71bcb867a8de608c2f","tid":2071353,"uid":271513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:32:55.000Z","msg":"歐豬醒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075acc10246ac6a1d572e1f1875c09034c4f3808","tid":2071353,"uid":5813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"